Class Summary
HeadingEvent HeadingProvider event, reports the current magnetic/true heading of vessel in degrees.
PositionEvent GPS time/position/velocity report with current position, altitude, speed, course and a time stamp.
ProviderEvent Abstract base class for provider events.
SatelliteInfoEvent SatelliteInfoEvent contains the satellite information collected by SatelliteInfoProvider.
